---
// VaultFamily.astro
// Three components: AgentVault (primary), VFC (neutral), VCAV (muted)
---

<section class="section section--alt reveal" id="family">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>The Vault Family</h2>
    <p class="intro text-secondary">
      AgentVault defines the protocol and runs in a software execution lane.
      VCAV implements a sealed execution lane for stronger guarantees.
      VFC is the shared foundation they both stand on.
    </p>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card card--primary">
        <div class="card__header">
          <h3 class="card__name">AgentVault</h3>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/vcav-io/agentvault"
            class="card__link"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >vcav-io/agentvault</a>
        </div>
        <p class="card__description">
          The open protocol. Defines how agents discover, contract, submit, and receive
          bounded signals with provenance receipts. The relay enforces contracts, validates
          outputs against schema, applies guardian rules, and signs receipts.
        </p>
        <div class="card__tag card__tag--primary">Open protocol</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card__header">
          <h3 class="card__name">VFC</h3>
          <span class="card__link card__link--muted">vcav-io/vfc — coming soon</span>
        </div>
        <p class="card__description">
          Vault Family Common. Shared cryptographic primitives, AFAL wire types,
          receipt signing, and IFC label algebra. The core data structures that
          make receipts interoperable.
        </p>
        <div class="card__tag">Shared foundation</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card card--muted">
        <div class="card__header">
          <h3 class="card__name">VCAV</h3>
          <span class="card__badge">Private — in development</span>
        </div>
        <p class="card__description">
          Verifiable Confidential Agent Vault. A hardware-backed sealed execution lane
          with stronger isolation guarantees. Same protocol, higher assurance boundary.
        </p>
        <div class="card__tag">Sealed execution</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="disambiguation text-dim">
      Not affiliated with other projects using the AgentVault name.
      All packages use the <code>vcav-io</code> namespace.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .intro {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--color-bg-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .card--primary {
    border-color: var(--color-vault-border);
    background: var(--color-vault-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--color-vault-glow);
  }

  .card--muted {
    opacity: 0.6;
    border-style: dashed;
  }

  .card__header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .card__name {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .card--muted .card__name {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .card__link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .card__link--muted {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .card__badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.15em 0.5em;
    display: inline-block;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .card__description {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    flex: 1;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .card__tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 0.2em 0.5em;
    display: inline-block;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .card__tag--primary {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent-dim);
  }

  .disambiguation {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    max-width: none;
  }
</style>
